            <_.fcp.TableDescription.true...table-description>
              <formatted-text>
                <run bold='true'>Diabetes 30-Day Hospital Readmission Risk Analysis</run>
                <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                <run>This dashboard analyzes diabetic inpatient encounters admitted through the emergency department to explore factors associated with 30-day hospital readmission risk. The analysis uses demographic, clinical, and healthcare utilization data to examine patterns in patient characteristics, hospital utilization, and readmission outcomes.</run>
                <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                <run>The project applies data analytics and machine learning methods to better understand factors related to readmission risk and communicate healthcare insights through interactive visualizations.</run>
              </formatted-text>
            </_.fcp.TableDescription.true...table-description>
          </object>
        </objects>
